  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/78ea8be98e3895dc23eab0589155c0d4.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Ballard roll through the danger filled levels towards the house of Ballerina, the love of his life!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/5f6170c52ba13fd8c903cd0180cf1e77.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AtmaSphere is roll-a-ball game set in a medieval world filled with <br>dangerous traps and uncertain paths! Roll all you want, but be careful not to fall off!<br></li><li>Collect all the diamonds to impress Ballerina and pick up yellow coins for bragging points!<br></li><li>But be careful, as you progress through the levels they become harder and more challenging, your skills will be tested by a variety of engaging traps and puzzles</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/ed41ac2214bcde435e9426170a03958d.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30 challenging, handcrafted levels!<br></li><li> Forgiving yet challenging gameplay!<br></li><li> Unique visual style paired with soothing sounds of rain in the background gives a beautiful relaxing \"atmasphere\" :^)<br></li><li> With every level comes a unique, wonderful soundtrack!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/b28f8ebbb4738d51fb75cce21140ff0b.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Steam Trading Cards</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/1b7cc13d946add59e42696fdb3ae4d20.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><br><strong><u>Join Ballard on the adventure and overcome all nasty troubles and help them become one!</u></strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/78ea8be98e3895dc23eab0589155c0d4.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Ballard roll through the danger filled levels towards the house of Ballerina, the love of his life!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/5f6170c52ba13fd8c903cd0180cf1e77.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AtmaSphere is roll-a-ball game set in a medieval world filled with <br>dangerous traps and uncertain paths! Roll all you want, but be careful not to fall off!<br></li><li>Collect all the diamonds to impress Ballerina and pick up yellow coins for bragging points!<br></li><li>But be careful, as you progress through the levels they become harder and more challenging, your skills will be tested by a variety of engaging traps and puzzles</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/ed41ac2214bcde435e9426170a03958d.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30 challenging, handcrafted levels!<br></li><li> Forgiving yet challenging gameplay!<br></li><li> Unique visual style paired with soothing sounds of rain in the background gives a beautiful relaxing \"atmasphere\" :^)<br></li><li> With every level comes a unique, wonderful soundtrack!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/b28f8ebbb4738d51fb75cce21140ff0b.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Steam Trading Cards</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/753660/extras/1b7cc13d946add59e42696fdb3ae4d20.webp?t=1772894098\" width=500 height=48 /></span><br><br><strong><u>Join Ballard on the adventure and overcome all nasty troubles and help them become one!</u></strong>",
